{"tid":2018674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[東網] 抗疫見成效　泰國將中港澳及南韓剔出疫區名單","createTime":"2020-05-15T18:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T10:44:47.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae231126b62d03066e0ae19c75c92a0fdad18bb","tid":2018674,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:14:54.000Z","msg":"[東網] 抗疫見成效 泰國將中港澳及南韓剔出疫區名單<br />\n05月16日(六) 00:00<br />\n<br />\n因應新冠肺炎疫情爆發，泰國自3月起將多地列入「危險傳染病疫區」。當地《王室公報》周五（15日）頒布，由本周六（16日）起將中國、香港、澳門及南韓剔出疫區名單，意味上述四地人士入境泰國，將毋須再出示醫學健康證明等。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200516/bkn-20200516000046263-0516_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200516%2Fbkn-20200516000046263-0516_00952_001.html&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=b7952519\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200516/bkn-20200516000046263-0516_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可惜從泰國回港還是需隔離14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係的話很多人肯定狗衝去泰國旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a5162aa5fab990ccf556db8d02a9817694d00edd","tid":2018674,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"剔出支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14344ce7e4d74571a09a79373fdaaab17fa43da4","tid":2018674,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"［國際戰線］抗議中國與建水壩致東南亞發生旱災<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2018627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2018627</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n拍爛擋 幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0afd4e19050b338cc65a69de5303102e34d2c61","tid":2018674,"uid":228995,